  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>The skin of a shaman who selects the stone spirit takes on a rough, stony appearance. When the shaman calls upon one of this spirit’s abilities, tiny gemstones underneath her flesh pulse with a bright glow, like phosphorescent geodes glittering in a dark cave.</em><br><br><strong>Spirit Magic Spells:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.fv9mgob508qv99zz]{Magic Stone} (1st),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.gqtg9ruv8kkd0knf]{Stone Call} (2nd),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.dkv9v4verb82fmpx]{Meld into Stone} (3rd),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.l83djt5019ujasjh]{Wall Of Stone} (4th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.knyako6zopc1chrv]{Stoneskin} (5th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wgm8mm1za909pwch]{Stone Tell} (6th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.g52zx1t1giteg5h1]{Statue} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.oeemcnfjod9zd7my]{Repel Metal or Stone} (8th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.o8jhvddxgunzx94i]{Clashing Rocks} (9th)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Spirit Animal: </strong>The shaman’s spirit animal looks as though it’s made out of earth and stone, with tiny gemstones embedded in its flesh. The animal gains DR 5/adamantine.</p>",
